    methodology: `This calculator compares two wealth-access strategies: selling appreciated assets (triggering capital gains tax) versus borrowing against them via a Securities-Based Line of Credit (SBLOC).

**Tax Drag Calculation:**
Tax Drag = Sale Amount × Marginal Capital Gains Rate
- US: 0%, 15%, or 20% + 3.8% NIIT (depending on income)
- UK: 18% (basic) or 24% (higher) on gains above £3,000 annual exempt
